{"tid":2461432,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"認真介紹　手機俠　五大看點","createTime":"2021-03-25T11:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T16:38:12.000Z","uid":69866,"like":16,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f2dded7ddd979552e8341c020850c7fe7e1b47","tid":2461432,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"相信好多朋友都對「手機俠」三個字唔陌生，到底呢套係一套咩類型既作品呢？我地一齊黎探討下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《帶著智慧型手機闖蕩異世界。》是冬原パトラ所作的日本輕小說作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5s2P3ZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5s2P3ZQ.jpg&h=006dfa7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d96UwxC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd96UwxC.jpg&h=4a228b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機俠精華！十分鐘看完上半季！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XLSxmogDdns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXLSxmogDdns&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=1d621067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XLSxmogDdns</a><br />\n（如果覺得太長可以set做兩倍速度，手機俠精華！５分半鐘看完上半季！）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>❶作品核心設定：魔法設計、廣闊世界觀、經典ＡＣＧ元素</strong></span><br />\n魔法分為　六種屬性魔法　和　無屬性魔法<br />\n七種屬性　為　水、火、土、風、光、暗<br />\n<br />\n屬性魔法係借助世界的自然力量所施放，而無屬性魔法則偏向個人。<br />\n<br />\n屬性魔法唔係個個人都用得，要睇天份，天生的。所以本身就有三種屬性相性既人已經係嬴在起跑線。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">手機俠既設定可以套用至任何作品！萌王既惡魔召喚，骨王的不死族生成，都係屬暗屬性魔法。雷切／千鳥呢啲空氣震動就係風屬性魔法。黑色五葉草世界樹魔法就係土屬性魔法。\n記憶操作，物質變更（黑色五葉草格雷），呢啲非自然力量既現象控制，就係無屬性魔法。\n\n無屬性魔法係唔同既作品都有出現。《Re:Zero》既加護就係常駐型無屬性魔法，每個人唔同，天生。萊因哈魯特就係當中既最強。不過因為手機俠個世界魔法層次未去到咁高，所以冇加護既設定。\n另一套講無屬性魔法既作品就係《葬送的芙莉蓮》。無屬性魔法學唔到只係人既資質問題。當然仲係因為量好大。\n（火系既話你識入門就可以自己develop落去，精通哂成個火系魔法，無屬性魔法唔得）\n芙莉蓮一路旅行學習既大多都係無屬性魔法。例如捕鳥魔法。\n至於點解《七龍珠》入面孫悟空要三年先學識學瞬間移動，因為係無屬性魔法黎。\n《平職》入面七大神代魔法都係無屬性魔法。\n萌王既神之怒就係水+光既複合魔法。無心者就係暗魔法。\n</code></pre><br />\n（注１：呢套作品未有「氣」、「武技」等元素。）<br />\n（注２：呢套作品未有無詠唱既出現。雖然手機功用上有啲似）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7kQ1GlO5grI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7kQ1GlO5grI&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=e9eefc15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7kQ1GlO5grI</a><br />\n透明魔法「invisible」同harry potter一樣，只係改變光線，唔能夠消聲。<br />\n結界可以封鎖針對空間既魔法，但封鎖唔到針對人類五感既魔法。<br />\n透明魔法「invisible」屬光屬性魔法，原因係佢係控制自然界既光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左魔法，仲有過去、未來、東方、西方等等既設定。<br />\n當然仲有其他穿越者。<br />\n<br />\n日本：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZdPkdN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZdPkdN.jpg&h=f8283d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UxaYX0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxaYX0K.png&h=2b7dadcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科幻及現代科技：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fyr6yB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fyr6yB.jpg&h=784b4d19&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxSXtQq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxSXtQq.jpg&h=d40db686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80LaO7Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80LaO7Z.jpg&h=8f7caec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtt38Nj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqtt38Nj.jpg&h=e208c145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劍與魔法世界的ＲＰＧ屠龍：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5jffv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5jffv6.jpg&h=ef6ba954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YV4iX1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYV4iX1Y.png&h=ed473fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n史萊姆／觸手：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2PShGq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2PShGq.jpg&h=2eb31ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18swyeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18swyeL.jpg&h=d84a8637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3pKTeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3pKTeL.jpg&h=9208db82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnEnFgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnEnFgf.jpg&h=3cc98f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n奶油犬：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzVaOP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzVaOP0.jpg&h=2b530b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泳衣＆褔利：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41aaO3j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41aaO3j.jpg&h=26a03e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Pvuj6C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Pvuj6C.gif&h=8303dedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WcCc2jY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWcCc2jY.gif&h=ac7ac6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmichTi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmichTi.gif&h=ee4e5fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyc1bbO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkyc1bbO.gif&h=23fa7032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他穿越者：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLp66LQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLp66LQ.jpg&h=159db7be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>❷由神明所致的死亡穿越</strong></span><br />\n因為本身就係神明做錯事，唔係主角強出頭被人吉死，或者俾卡車撞死，所以神明對住佢都好低聲下氣。但係主角實在太看破紅塵，令神明好驚訝。<br />\n因為主角實在太好人，唔止俾佢用手機，仲幫佢開掛。同其他作品唔同，無任何力量限制，要求等等，唔洗打魔王，唔洗做勇者，唔洗拜神。<br />\n因為呢個設定，故事發展可以有無限可能性。同類型無限伸延的作品有：《異世界迷宮黑心企業》（迷宮ブラックカンパニー）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qrqBKES.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqrqBKES.png&h=9dd604b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oUnFbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oUnFbV.jpg&h=03e94ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEZ66Sn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEZ66Sn.jpg&h=e2b32b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50X8ALQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50X8ALQ.jpg&h=053e9a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>❸Slip</strong></span><br />\n愈簡單既魔法愈有效。對比起同類型作品，往往都要推陳出新，但係呢套只係用一招就可以由頭嬴到落尾。Slip係冇任何對抗手段，所有防衛魔法都失效。<br />\n有啲似一拳超人，簡單直接唔會輸。<br />\n當然無屬性魔法本身唔係攻擊用，仲要配合其他魔法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZ1EHvt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZ1EHvt.jpg&h=988ae2da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mf2sRck.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMf2sRck.jpg&h=c7b7fd61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>❹豐富人設</strong></span><br />\n人物設定十分豐富，各種屬性都有。<br />\n姊妹：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbivONF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbivONF.jpg&h=056f2dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBqBKCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBqBKCZ.jpg&h=92cb0c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真宮寺櫻／博麗靈夢：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6DS2eu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6DS2eu.png&h=606c1574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R9q94sP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=